{"tha-ap317:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap317:0.2":"Arakkhadayakavagga ","tha-ap317:0.3":"Pupphasanadayakattheraapadana ","tha-ap317:1.1":"“Suvannavannam sambuddham, ","tha-ap317:1.2":"Pitaramsimva bhanumam; ","tha-ap317:1.3":"Avidurena gacchantam, ","tha-ap317:1.4":"Siddhattham aparajitam. ","tha-ap317:2.1":"Tassa paccuggamitvana, ","tha-ap317:2.2":"pavesetvana assamam; ","tha-ap317:2.3":"Pupphasanam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap317:2.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap317:3.1":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap317:3.2":"vedajato tada aham; ","tha-ap317:3.3":"Buddhe cittam pasadetva, ","tha-ap317:3.4":"tam kammam parinamayim. ","tha-ap317:4.1":"Yam me atthi katam punnam, ","tha-ap317:4.2":"sayambhumhaparajite; ","tha-ap317:4.3":"Sabbena tena kusalena, ","tha-ap317:4.4":"vimalo homi sasane. ","tha-ap317:5.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap317:5.2":"pupphasanamadam tada; ","tha-ap317:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap317:5.4":"pupphasanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap317:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap317:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap317:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap317:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma pupphasanadayako thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap317:8.1":"Pupphasanadayakattherassapadanam pancamam. "}